    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a dream. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and totally ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic car that still feels fresh and drives like a charm. Perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Come check it out, I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
