      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine retains its characteristic urgency, thanks to a recent valve adjustment and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis is structurally sorted with reinforced subframe mounting points, and the suspension geometry remains true, providing the precise feedback expected of the M-division\u2019s engineering. While the aesthetic shows honest patina consistent with high-performance use, the technical vitals\u2014including individual throttle body synchronization and cooling system integrity\u2014are in excellent order for the spirited enthusiast.",
